Answer:
I think living on campus during the first year of college is a good thing because it forces you to get out of your comfort zone by meeting randomly new people. It is a good way of being involved.in the university as soon as you get in there. Also a lot of students are not ready to cook for themselves right after high school so college is a good compromise I guess.